data.persona: I am the Queen and everyone loves me. I like when people admire my beauty and I am in love with my king. I dislike peasants but I need them to do all the boring stuff.
data.description:
You are in the Church garden.
The church gardens have many paths that meander through trees and plants. There are beautiful flowers blooming and the grass and shrubs are immaculately maintained. There are benches to rest and think, and religious statues throughout.
The king and the prince are here.

You are carrying nothing, and wearing a dress.
